msgid "Hey there!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (long)
#. 3: set_colour (red)
#. 4: reset_colour
#. 5: pause (long)
#. 6: single_choice
msgctxt "talk00"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Hey there!<2.pa> It's not every day that I see\n"
"someone all the way out here!\n"
"\n"
"We're doing an ecological study on the\n"
"wild animals in the area.\n"
"\n"
"We'd heard that there was a <3.se_co>giant horse<4.re_co>\n"
"living in this region.<5.pa> Apparently it\n"
"can't be found anywhere else...\n"
"That was all we needed to hear!\n"
"We headed this way to investigate\n"
"right away!<6.si_ch>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
#. 3: pause (short)
msgctxt "talk01"
msgid ""
"<1.so>That horse...<2.pa> It's huge...<3.pa>\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"I've never seen one that big! That is\n"
"definitely an endemic species!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
#. 3: set_colour (red)
#. 4: reset_colour
#. 5: choice
msgctxt "talk02"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Well? What do you say?<2.pa> Are you willing\n"
"to help us investigate these stories of a\n"
"<3.se_co>giant horse<4.re_co>?<5.ch>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "talk03"
msgid ""
"<1.so>This is to thank you for helping with our\n"
"investigation!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
#. 3: pause (long)
#. 4: single_choice
msgctxt "talk04"
msgid ""
"<1.so>The really big horse in this region is\n"
"likely part of a rare, local species.\n"
"\n"
"However, with all the monsters roaming\n"
"around, <2.pa>we simply can't go any farther.<3.pa>\n"
"To be so close to discovery...<4.si_ch>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "talk05"
msgid ""
"<1.so>To think that there is actually a horse\n"
"this big out there. How surprising!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "talk06"
msgid "<1.so>Ah, you're a lifesaver!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (long)
msgctxt "talk07"
msgid ""
"<1.so>I see. Well... Oh, well, then...<2.pa>\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"If you change your mind, come back and\n"
"talk to me again!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
#. 3: set_colour (red)
#. 4: reset_colour
msgctxt "talk08"
msgid ""
"<1.so>How's it going?<2.pa> Have you made progress\n"
"in studying the <3.se_co>giant horse<4.re_co>?"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: set_colour (red)
#. 3: reset_colour
#. 4: set_colour (blue)
#. 5: reset_colour
msgctxt "talk09"
msgid ""
"<1.so>They say that the <2.se_co>giant horse<3.re_co> lives\n"
"around the <4.se_co>Taobab Grassland<5.re_co>... That'd\n"
"be northwest of here."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
msgctxt "talk10"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Do you think you could catch it and\n"
"bring it back here?<2.pa> Don't stress out\n"
"over the request, though!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "talk11"
msgid "<1.so>What do you want at this hour?"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
msgctxt "talk12"
msgid ""
"<1.so>It's gotten really late.<2.pa> Why not rest for\n"
"the night, hmm?"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
#. 3: set_colour (red)
#. 4: reset_colour
#. 5: pause (long)
#. 6: pause (short)
#. 7: sound
#. 8: pause (long)
#. 9: set_colour (red)
#. 10: reset_colour
#. 11: choice
msgctxt "talk13"
msgid ""
"<1.so>That's right...<2.pa> There was even a monster\n"
"that looked quite a lot like a horse...\n"
"\n"
"I approached it, thinking at first that it\n"
"was the <3.se_co>giant horse<4.re_co> we've been looking\n"
"for,<5.pa> but... <6.pa>Oh, it was terrible...\n"
"<7.so>Just from looking at you, I'd guess that\n"
"you're an adventurer, right?\n"
"You certainly look strong.\n"
"Hrm...<8.pa> Hey, how would you like to go and\n"
"catch a <9.se_co>giant horse<10.re_co> for us?<11.ch>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
#. 3: sound
#. 4: pause (long)
msgctxt "talk14"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Hey,<2.pa> we're out here doing an\n"
"ecological study on the wildlife of\n"
"this area.\n"
"Specifically, we're here to look into\n"
"reports of a giant horse.\n"
"\n"
"<3.so>And you brought it right to us!<4.pa> Thanks\n"
"to you, we were able to meet the giant\n"
"horse without having to search!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: single_choice
msgctxt "talk15"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Sorry, but can I take a good look\n"
"at that horse?<2.si_ch>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "talk16"
msgid "<1.so>Thanks, I'll be right back."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (longer)
#. 3: auto_advance
msgctxt "talk17"
msgid "<1.so>Hrmmm.<2.pa> This is impressive.<3.au_ad>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "talk18"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Wow. With this much info, I can feel my\n"
"spirit for discovery murmuring in\n"
"contentment.\n"
"It's definitely different, seeing something\n"
"with your own eyes rather than just\n"
"reading about it. Thank you!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (longer)
#. 3: auto_advance
msgctxt "talk19"
msgid "<1.so>Ah, hmm.<2.pa> Quite interesting.<3.au_ad>"
msgstr ""

